{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_07_03",
  "title": "白石千紗 3話 お父さんと一緒に",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、見て下さい！\nうまく金魚をすくえました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ look!\nI caught a goldfish successfully!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9829689401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "凄いじゃないか\n千紗がこんなに上手だとは思わなかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's amazing.\nI didn't expect Chisa to be this good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.2333333016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "お父さんが金魚すくいが得意で\nやり方を教わったことがあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My dad is good at goldfish scooping‚ so\nhe taught me how to do it once.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.949500529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりだったけど、{user}さんに\nいいところを見せられて良かった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been a while‚ but I'm glad I could\nshow you something nice‚ {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4161671321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "あっ……でも、寮で金魚飼えるのかなぁ？\n水槽もないし……お店に返した方がいいでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… But can we have goldfish in the dorm?\nWe don't have a tank… Should I return it to the store?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.5828354519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "飼いたいのなら、みんなに相談してみたらどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you want to keep it‚ why not ask everyone for advice?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.7161689123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……。みんなに聞いてみます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right… I'll ask everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.0539225102,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（夜店で遊ぶ千紗はとてもいい笑顔をしている）\n（今の千紗を見たら、きっと父親ならこう言うだろうな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Chisa playing at the festival has a really nice smile.）\n（If her dad saw her like this‚ he'd probably say something like that.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.3333413125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "千紗。今日の浴衣、よく似合ってて凄く可愛いよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ that yukata suits you so well today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.087397782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "ふぇっ！？\nど、どうしたんですか、急にそんなこと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!?\nW-why are you suddenly saying that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3844490527,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9666.6679382,
          "startTime": 62.0511169909
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9666.6679382,
          "startTime": 62.0511169909
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9666.6679382,
          "startTime": 62.0511169909
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あの……私あっちでヨーヨー釣りやってきますね！\n今度はあれを――きゃあっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ um… I'll go do some yo-yo fishing over there!\nNext time I'll… Kyaa!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9177836576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "千紗！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.5177826403,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2454.2856216000073,
          "startTime": 65.9720682619
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-night",
      "startTime": 65.4720682619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……\n転んでヨーヨー釣りの水槽に落ちちゃうなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh…\nFalling and landing in the yo-yo fishing tank…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.2054089704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-night",
      "startTime": 73.372075637
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "浴衣もびしょ濡れで\n{user}さんもきっと呆れてるよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My yukata is soaked‚ too…\n{user}-san must be really disappointed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.872075637,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2980.867783400001,
          "startTime": 78.8529434204
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "おっ、着替えて戻ってきたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you changed and came back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-night",
      "startTime": 82.1756825922
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、{user}さん？\nもしかして、私を待っててくれたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ {user}-san?\nCould it be… you were waiting for me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7423492589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "すみません\nせっかくみんなで楽しんでたのに、私のせいで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry.\nEveryone was having fun together‚ but because of me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.3423492589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-night",
      "startTime": 94.9090159255
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "誰も気にしてないよ\nそれより、これ、千紗に買っておいたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No one minds.\nMore importantly‚ I bought this for you‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0666728656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-night",
      "startTime": 100.6940043924
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "それは……わたあめ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is… cotton candy…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.6940043924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-night",
      "startTime": 103.8273377257
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "千紗はこれが好きじゃないかと思って……\n夏祭りでよく買って食べたって前に話してくれただろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought you liked it‚ Chisa.\nDidn't you say you used to buy and eat it at summer festivals?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.0000061989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "覚えていてくれたんですね\nありがとうございます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You remembered that for me?\nThank you very much…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.431351264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-night",
      "startTime": 115.4980148789
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　もしかして、わたあめは好きじゃなかったか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? Didn't you actually like cotton candy?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.4980148789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、大好きです。ただ、一人じゃ食べきれなくて\nいつもお父さんやお姉ちゃんと分けていたので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I love it. But I couldn't finish it alone\nbecause I always shared it with my dad or sister…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.1062687234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-night",
      "startTime": 129.1729348815
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さんと\n半分こ、してもいいですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "… {user}-san‚\ncould we split it in half?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.5729348815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "構わないよ。じゃあ、二人で食べながら歩こうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't mind. Shall we walk and eat together then?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.1729348815,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6399.534988400006,
          "startTime": 142.5724698699
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-night",
      "startTime": 142.0391365365
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん\n今日は付き合ってくれてありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "… {user}-san.\nThank you for accompanying me today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.5058238026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "おかげで元気が出ました\nお祭りなんだから、遠慮してたらもったいないですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to you‚ I feel much better now.\nSince it's a festival‚ it would be a waste to hold back‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.6058238026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-night",
      "startTime": 156.0724904693
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "お祭りでやりたいことがまだまだあるんです\n夏の思い出、いっぱい作りましょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are still so many things I want to do at the festival.\nLet's create lots of summer memories together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.4391571359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-night",
      "startTime": 162.8724904693
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、俺に手伝えることがあれば遠慮なく言ってくれ\n今日は俺が千紗の父親がわりなんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ if there's anything I can help with‚ just let me know.\nToday‚ I'll be like Chisa's dad‚ so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.1666652362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "お父さんのかわり……\nじゃあ、はぐれないように手を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like my dad…\nThen‚ can I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.0628533677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-night",
      "startTime": 178.3295403792
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
