      "text": "それじゃあ……えいっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright then… Here I go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.7868056291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（なんだかほっとけないような、目が離せないような）\n（……娘を持つってこんな気持ちなのかな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Somehow‚ I can't leave her alone‚ can't take my eyes off her.）\n（…Is this what it feels like to have a daughter?）",
