      "text": "どうかしましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is something wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.1536029808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "いや、なんでもない。ちゃんと掴んだな？\n俺から離れないように、しっかりついてくるんだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's nothing. Are you holding on properly?\nJust stay close to me and don't let go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.2333563166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-night",
      "startTime": 208.605076948
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
