      "text": "そういえばりんご飴も好きだと言っていたな\nでも、わたあめもあるし、もう食べられないんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ you said you liked candy apples too.\nBut we already have cotton candy‚ so maybe we can't eat any more…",
