      "text": "（家族と一緒に歩いている気分なのか？）\n（今夜の千紗はいつもより表情が柔らかい気がするな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Feels like walking with family?）\n（Chisa's expression tonight seems softer than usual.）",
        "id": ""
      },
